# Aakhara

**आखाड़ा** — voice sales-training roleplay for Business Development Executives. The practice arena where BDEs sharpen their pitch before every real call.

**Status**: pre-launch
**Brand**: Vagary Labs (tech/R&D division of Vagary Life Pvt Ltd)
**Domain**: `aakhara.com` (pending purchase)
**Positioning**: TBD — standalone OR Vagary Voice sub-product (operator decides)

## What this repo is

Currently: **landing page** for Aakhara.
Eventually: full voice-roleplay app surface (when voice-stack integration lands).

## Voice stack (planned)

| Component | Vendor | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| Speech-to-text | Deepgram | Nova-3 vs Base — operator-Q on budget tier |
| Text-to-speech | ElevenLabs | Hindi + English voices for India BDE market |
| Roleplay LLM | Gemini 2.5 Flash or OpenAI GPT-4o | Low-latency conversational |

## Brand identity

The Sanskrit word **आखाड़ा** (aakhara) means a traditional Indian wrestling/practice arena — a place of disciplined sparring before the real fight. Aakhara brings that philosophy to sales: practice the call before you're on the call.

- **Primary**: sienna-earth `#A0522D`
- **Secondary**: chocolate `#D2691E`
- **Accent**: wheat `#F5DEB3`
- **Brand surface**: saddle-brown `#8B4513`

See `docs/design/` for full token system + component fork notes from `host_page`.

